{"tid":775560,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"或者人人都有啲 Depression?","createTime":"2018-08-11T09:14:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-11T09:22:08.000Z","uid":62970,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"596f20490a6afa31872ccdc2a433f1000f654caf","tid":775560,"uid":62970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T09:14:22.000Z","msg":"///抑鬱症可由神經傳遞物質血清素（Serotonin）失調引發，或因慣性負面想法不斷循環而造成身心徵狀<br />\n<br />\n特別徵狀<br />\n抑鬱症有別於其他生理疾病，徵狀通常不明顯。患者自己未必能就察覺徵狀，身邊家人朋友的觀察，對發現抑鬱症十分重要。抑鬱症最明顯的徵狀包括:<br />\n<br />\n1. 思想悲觀，認為人生沒有希望<br />\n2. 情緒低落<br />\n3. 對事物失去興趣<br />\n<br />\n這些負面情緒與正常情緒低落的最大分別，在於抑鬱症患者無法看穿情緒的<span style=\"color: red;\">暫時性</span>，認為以後都不會快樂，而這種想法影響日常生活（如對事物提不起興趣、工作效率受影響)///<br />\n<br />\n有無人啱啱畢業，進入呢個社會，<br />\n對身邊幾乎所有野都失去興趣？<br />\n而且，覺得起碼未來十年都會係咁嘅狀態？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c570cf9140dad95a3b589c03c7f6ed861c7e847a","tid":775560,"uid":33885,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T09:16:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3211dfb93425a0d4d1274db093c98164002e273f","tid":775560,"uid":48213,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c570cf9140dad95a3b589c03c7f6ed861c7e847a","tid":775560,"uid":33885,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T09:16:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T09:20:26.000Z","msg":"呢度都要互含？"},{"pid":"72838c7475d9075cf865b281d3d7987427204d79","tid":775560,"uid":33885,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3211dfb93425a0d4d1274db093c98164002e273f","tid":775560,"uid":48213,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c570cf9140dad95a3b589c03c7f6ed861c7e847a","tid":775560,"uid":33885,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T09:16:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T09:20:26.000Z","msg":"呢度都要互含？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T09:22:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}